            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper is soft, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
